01/03/2011
ZAGREB, Croatia -- Several hundred people gathered on Monday (February 28th) in downtown Zagreb for another anti-government rally. 
They tried to reach the government building but were stopped by the police. 
The rally ended peacefully. 
Several anti-government demonstrations organised via Facebook were staged in Zagreb last week. 
(Hina, Poslovni Dnevnik, Index.hr, tportal.hr - 28/02/11)
